      *----------------------------------------------------------------*00082100
                                                                        00082200
       01 WRK-NUMEROS.                                                  00082300
          05 WRK-NUM1                       PIC S9(03)      VALUE ZEROS.00082400
          05 WRK-NUM2                       PIC S9(03)      VALUE ZEROS.00082500
          05 WRK-NUM3                       PIC S9(03)      VALUE ZEROS.00082600
          05 WRK-MAIOR                      PIC X(15)      VALUE SPACES.00082700
                                                                        00082800
       77 WRK-FLAG                          PIC 9(01)       VALUE ZEROS.00082900
       77 WRK-ERRO                          PIC X(30)      VALUE SPACES.00083000
                                                                        00083100
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*00083200
                                                                        00083300
      *================================================================*00083400
       PROCEDURE                            DIVISION.                   00083500
